title: Healthy and Delicious
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Organic, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Healthier food concept restaurant offering fresh salads, Mexican style wraps, paninis, organic teas, and more; the meats offered are chicken and tuna. Vegan choices include a grilled veggies over organic brown rice and the Southwest dish with organic brown rice, black beans, tortilla chips, onion, and avocado. Other dishes could be made vegan upon request. Has Wi-Fi. Opened in summer 2013.
